summary:
Technically advance at the core of the Internet Marketing field , SEO marketing Specialist for more than 15 years of experienced. Possess excellent Marketing business and communication skills and can consult SEO tecnically with influence at all high level aspects in Internet Marketing.

Develop marketing strategies such as:
Develops and analyze websites that needs to be improved an advance organic way or revised, keyword mapping and website structuring for best results in Google and other SE's. audit website and do the SILO's structures strategically. off-page and on-page meta tags, titles, description gaps and blind spots, URL's, keyword density. with high quality SEO content, PageRank monitoring and Marketing campaign. support backlinks to improve website ranking, online coaching, blogs and web design, graphics. we make sure that we keep up to date with the latest SEO updates and algorithm.
